Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.08,0:00:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是母亲的资料文件而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.04,0:00:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.06,0:00:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是最新世代的NEO-GIN的母体遗传基因提供者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是玛丽亚的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 兑现了承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.70,0:00:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们来检查一下现在装备了CloneBlade的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你很期待哦 玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.78,0:00:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是最完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.46,0:00:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不能在一起呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩溃在继续着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也确认了精神状态产生混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.70,0:03:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没有预想中的深刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许和之前崩溃的志织一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说这就是这次想要确认的所谓母亲的感情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是咖啡奶酒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:04:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里好安静呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是我父亲建造的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.53,0:04:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是在安慰我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不说的好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算联络上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在在什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.89,0:04:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之　你马上去接梨穂子回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NswF的那些姐妹不单只是由被选择的遗传基因出生而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们自己也被作为母体提供遗传基因
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.62,0:05:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是闻所未闻的近亲交配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近亲? 什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 所有姐妹的父亲的遗传基因都是一个人提供的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进而 下个世代的姐妹们也是用相同的父亲的遗传基因 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于那个男人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些姐妹即是女儿也是妻子 还是孙女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据我猜测 那个父亲就是教父 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这么做我是不知道 但一定不是些什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管离NswF有多远
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.84,0:05:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稣峰玲奈也是姐妹中的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那家伙不是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把梨穂子带回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她和那种怪物在一起的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.19,0:05:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正·胸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有要回来的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.33,0:06:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么资格啊 明明那么担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说Lady是怪物 要我把梨穂子接回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.45,0:06:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有资格这么说人家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady救过梨穂子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两次了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有钱 又是医生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说 她是真正的妈妈呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我来 她才能让梨穂子更加幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的这么想的话 就没有必要再烦恼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃早饭了哦 玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天西田先生有公事外出 今天就休息一天好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想要出去买东西的话派车送你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.28,0:07:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了我在房间玩就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那就老老实实的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.47,0:07:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那是玛丽亚的妈妈 一定要玛丽亚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拷贝个人资料是禁止的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是做个笔记而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能给外人看的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那张两人幽会的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你老婆看看会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 已经没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天好像身体不太好的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待着别动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:08:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blade的版本也不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陌生的面孔 也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.09,0:09:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是次世代的NEO-GIN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的女儿 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是玛丽亚的妈妈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个孩子很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.47,0:09:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知道她的来历
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资料中的那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道就是 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那是玛丽亚的姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这么矮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是自然分娩的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资料记录她已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是旧的纪录 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者 是故意篡改的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情随便它好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去停车场在汽车里等我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一下 坐下来慢慢说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去买东西  能在这里等一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.95,0:10:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 全部都是玛丽亚的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是骗人的 都是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不可能会发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  玛丽亚在训练还有学习都很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.15,0:11:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈是玛丽亚的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不是和玛丽亚在一起呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么多抱抱玛丽亚呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.31,0:11:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 有着惊人的力量 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 在这个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.37,0:12:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像现在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是X-CON? 还是NEO-GIN?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 是在远处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有着很强的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 走回去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.67,0:13:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.37,0:13:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打败她的可能性很低
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.64,0:13:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要多问 待在这里就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 我会回来接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才看上去稍微有点妈妈的感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二世代NEO-GIN的出现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.61,0:13:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定把梨穂子带到别的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 我会回来接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:13:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种没有根据的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是那么回事 遗传基因信息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在那边 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要让她消失 让开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈讨厌玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是我的妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈也给我…消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了 受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪…怪兽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穂子 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泽为什么你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多原因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉到了 梨穂子有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.55,0:15:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有妈妈的资格哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穂子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 不要躲呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不让我打中 玛丽亚要生气了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀 真让人失望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也有很香味道 但是去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泽 那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 那是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也许不知道 但是这种怪物是存在的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.51,0:16:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.21,0:17:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你们碰那孩子一根手指!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 已经不行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 接下来得让那个消失…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.77,0:17:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 不能理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不是我的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱用自己的力量是不行的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不弄清楚的话没有任何意义
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里 立刻回收
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:17:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外一台呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没这个必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你的妈妈正赶过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.78,0:18:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈她?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打败那些怪物 是你妈妈的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.52,0:18:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是妈妈不回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为妈妈已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.20,0:18:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那个家伙是为了谁在做这么危险的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 全都是为了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙一直都只是为了你而战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈她最喜欢梨穂子了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穂子!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.96,0:18:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.08,0:19:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.45,0:19:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穂子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穂子 有受伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玲奈吗 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的回收班已经在赶过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经 结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲奈 把那孩子交回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 研究已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.76,0:20:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.14,0:20:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 我第一次在战斗中感受到了快感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.69,0:20:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为崩溃还是因为要保护那个孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在研究着自己 结果…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却还是不能理解 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要理解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.91,0:20:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在以前 只是在一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.04,0:21:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你也产生了不能理解的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在那一瞬间…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穂子 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.82,0:23:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长先生说要带我们去海边玩  
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.48,0:23:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 目的虽然有的那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.22,0:23:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说斗泽的朋友的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.53,0:23:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比梨穂子稍微大一点孩子也会去 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.44,0:23:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人期待  
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.36,0:23:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前一直也没有带你去哪里玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.03,0:23:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始 会经常带你去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.46,0:23:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此妈妈会加油的
